{"lemma":"فاضِلَةٌ","slug":"فاضِلَةٌ","root":"ف.ض.ل","root_slug":"ف-ض-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ض-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","name"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34093"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%90%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of فَضَلَ (faḍala)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Fadil or Fadel"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb فَضَلَ (faḍala)."},"ipa":["/faː.dˤil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34093","headword_ar":"فَاضِلَةٌ","root":"fDl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faDiylapN","text_ar":"فَضِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as a concrete term, signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An excellent thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excel-lent action;"},{"kind":"text","text":"each as distinguished from an excel-lent quality]; (K, TA;) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fawaADilu","text_ar":"فَوَاضِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [but generally] it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that is given:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 431, and Har p. 184:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a benefit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefaction:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is continual,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uninterrupted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:) pl. as above: (Ham and Har, ubi suprà; and MA:) [or]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fawaADilu","text_ar":"فَوَاضِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefits,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefactions, that are goodly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as are great,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fawaADilu AlmaAli","text_ar":"فَوَاضِلُ المَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What accrues to one of the proceeds and profits of property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the increase of lands and palm-trees and the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the gains of commercial transactions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the milk and wool of cattle and sheep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) The Arabs say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA Eazaba AlmaAlu qal~ato fawaADiluhu","text_ar":"اـِذَا عَزَبَ المَالُ قَلَّتْ فَوَاضِلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When the estate is distant, the profits of its owner, accruing therefrom, are small in quantity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","MA","IDrd","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}